<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTM5.9.2">
<l>vaṅkamār kaṭalka ḷēḻum malaiyumvā ṉakamum maṟṟum</l>
<l>aṅkaṇmā ñāla mellā mamutucey tumiḻnta ventai</l>
<l>tiṅkaḷmā mukila ṇavu ceṟipoḻil teṉti ruppēr</l>
<l>eṅkaḷmā liṟaivaṉ nāma mēttinā ṉuynta vāṟē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>The way I was saved was by praising the name of god, our father who,</l>
<l>Having made food of everything - the great earth with beautiful places,</l>
<l>The seven wave-filled seas, mountains, the heavens, and the rest</l>
<l rend="indent"> - disgorged them,</l>
<l>Our Māl of Tiruppēr of the South with thick groves that reach</l>
<l rend="indent">up to the moon and dark clouds.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
